SUBSTITUTE FOR
HOUSE BILL NO. 4961
A bill to amend 1967 PA 281, entitled
"Income tax act of 1967,"
by amending sections 12, 30, 36, 607, 695, and 805 (MCL 206.12,
206.30, 206.36, 206.607, 206.695, and 206.805), sections 12, 607,
and 805 as amended by 2024 PA 177, sections 30 and 695 as amended
by 2023 PA 4, and section 36 as amended by 2011 PA 38; and to
repeal acts and parts of acts.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
