4 607.
5 (5) "Internal revenue code" means the United States internal
6 revenue code of 1986 in effect on January 1, 2021 2025 or, at the
7 option of the taxpayer, in effect for the tax year.
8 (6) "Member", when used in reference to a flow-through entity,
9 means a shareholder of an S corporation or a partner or member in a
10 partnership.
